%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> WO_PROPOSAL: MCSCH: WO Proposal - Roll Changeover
    
    WO_PROPOSAL --> TIMING_STORED: Apriso: Store Roll Changeover Timing Info
    TIMING_STORED --> EXECUTION_READY: Apriso: Ready for Execution
    
    EXECUTION_READY --> WO_EXECUTED: Apriso: WOs Executed
    WO_EXECUTED --> DOWNTIME_STARTED: Apriso: Downtime Started (Campaign Downtime)
    
    DOWNTIME_STARTED --> MO_CREATED: Apriso: MO Created and Sent
    MO_CREATED --> SAP_MO_CREATE: SAP: Create Maintenance Order
    
    SAP_MO_CREATE --> SAP_MO_CONFIRM: SAP: Confirm Maintenance Order
    SAP_MO_CONFIRM --> MAINTENANCE_EXECUTION: Maintenance Team: Execute Maintenance
    
    MAINTENANCE_EXECUTION --> DOWNTIME_COMPLETED: Apriso: Downtime Completed
    DOWNTIME_COMPLETED --> DUAL_CONFIRMATION: Apriso: Dual Confirmation
    
    DUAL_CONFIRMATION --> PRODUCTION_CONFIRM: Production Team: Confirm Completion
    DUAL_CONFIRMATION --> MAINTENANCE_CONFIRM: Maintenance Team: Confirm Completion
    
    PRODUCTION_CONFIRM --> SAP_DOWNTIME_WO: SAP: Create Downtime WO
    MAINTENANCE_CONFIRM --> SAP_DOWNTIME_WO
    
    SAP_DOWNTIME_WO --> DURATION_SAVED: MCSCH: Save Downtime Duration
    DURATION_SAVED --> REPLAN_CHECK: MCSCH: Check if Replan Needed
    
    REPLAN_CHECK --> REPLAN_MANUAL: Manual Replan if Needed
    REPLAN_MANUAL --> CAMPAIGN_RESUMED: Campaign Resumed
    REPLAN_CHECK --> CAMPAIGN_RESUMED: No Replan Needed
    
    CAMPAIGN_RESUMED --> [*]
    
    %% Unplanned downtime path
    EXECUTION_READY --> UNPLANNED_DOWNTIME: Unplanned Downtime Occurs
    UNPLANNED_DOWNTIME --> DOWNTIME_STARTED
    
    note right of WO_PROPOSAL
        Campaign Downtime Planning
        Roll Changeover WO
    end note
    
    note right of TIMING_STORED
        Roll Changeover Timing
        Stored in Apriso
    end note
    
    note right of DOWNTIME_STARTED
        Downtime Initiated
        Can be Unplanned
    end note
    
    note right of MO_CREATED
        Maintenance Order for
        Roll Regrinding
    end note
    
    note right of DUAL_CONFIRMATION
        Two-level Confirmation:
        Production & Maintenance
    end note
    
    note right of DURATION_SAVED
        Actual Downtime Duration
        Recorded for Analysis
    end note
    
    note right of REPLAN_CHECK
        Determine if Campaign
        Replanning is Needed
    end note
